---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  title="Privacy Policy | Archigiliti"
  description="Privacy policy for the Archigiliti website."
>
  <Section variant="light" class="pt-12 md:pt-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Last updated: February 2025</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">The data controller is Archigiliti, based in Poland. Contact: <a href="mailto:piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com</a></p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Scope of Data Collection</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">This website does not automatically collect any personal data. We do not use cookies for analytics or marketing purposes.</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Personal data (name, email address) is processed only when the user voluntarily provides it through email contact.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Data provided by users is used solely for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Responding to inquiries</li>
          <li>Business correspondence</li>
          <li>Preparing cooperation proposals</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. User Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Under GDPR, users have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Access their data</li>
          <li>Rectify data</li>
          <li>Erase data</li>
          <li>Restrict processing</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
          <li>Object to processing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">For data protection inquiries, please contact: <a href="mailto:piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
